originalText.text: I came here for covid testing. As I arrived, they directed me to the clinic to fill out the forms and then went to one of the trailers to register, then directed to another trailer for testing. One of the medical staff took my blood and took a sample from my nose, she was very gentle and kind. They told me my results will be back within 72 hours, but I got my results back the next day. I found the whole process very efficient and probably took less than 15 minutes.

originalText.text: I have now come here two separate times to get COVID tests. Both times the process was smooth and easy and all the staff was friendly as could be. It's awesome to know this place is here when reading how dysfunctional it can be elsewhere in the country.

originalText.text:
Get your COVID test here!! Everyone there for testing was properly distanced on the sidewalk and staff were super friendly. They even offered me a chair and cold water (I'm very pregnant). Wait time was about 20 minutes on a Tuesday AM and I got my results in 3 days.
